#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn15.5"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn15.5:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 15 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 15 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn15.5:0.2"
msgid "1. Paṭhamavagga "
msgstr "1. The First Chapter "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn15.5:0.3"
msgid "5. Pabbatasutta "
msgstr "5. A Mountain "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn15.5:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati … pe … ārāme … pe …. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn15.5:1.2"
msgid "Atha kho aññataro bhikkhu yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho so bhikkhu bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then a mendicant went up to the Buddha, bowed, sat down to one side, and asked him, "

msgctxt "sn15.5:1.3"
msgid "“kīvadīgho nu kho, bhante, kappo”ti? "
msgstr "“Sir, how long is an eon?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn15.5:1.4"
msgid "“Dīgho kho, bhikkhu, kappo. "
msgstr "“Mendicant, an eon is long. "

msgctxt "sn15.5:1.5"
msgid "So na sukaro saṅkhātuṃ ettakāni vassāni iti vā, ettakāni vassasatāni iti vā, ettakāni vassasahassāni iti vā, ettakāni vassasatasahassāni iti vā”ti. "
msgstr "It’s not easy to calculate how many years, how many hundreds or thousands or hundreds of thousands of years it lasts.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.182, sc2
msgctxt "sn15.5:2.1"
msgid "“Sakkā pana, bhante, upamaṃ kātun”ti? "
msgstr "“But sir, is it possible to give a simile?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn15.5:2.2"
msgid "“Sakkā, bhikkhū”ti bhagavā avoca. "
msgstr "“It’s possible,” said the Buddha. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn15.5:2.3"
msgid "“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhu, mahāselo pabbato yojanaṃ āyāmena yojanaṃ vitthārena yojanaṃ ubbedhena acchinno asusiro ekagghano. "
msgstr "“Suppose there was a huge stone mountain, a league long, a league wide, and a league high, with no cracks or holes, one solid mass. "

msgctxt "sn15.5:2.4"
msgid "Tamenaṃ puriso vassasatassa vassasatassa accayena kāsikena vatthena sakiṃ sakiṃ parimajjeyya. "
msgstr "And as each century passed someone would stroke it with a fine cloth from Kāsī. "

msgctxt "sn15.5:2.5"
msgid "Khippataraṃ kho so, bhikkhu, mahāselo pabbato iminā upakkamena parikkhayaṃ pariyādānaṃ gaccheyya, na tveva kappo. "
msgstr "By this means the huge stone mountain would be worn away before the eon comes to an end. "

msgctxt "sn15.5:2.6"
msgid "Evaṃ dīgho, bhikkhu, kappo. "
msgstr "That’s how long an eon is. "

msgctxt "sn15.5:2.7"
msgid "Evaṃ dīghānaṃ kho, bhikkhu, kappānaṃ neko kappo saṃsito, nekaṃ kappasataṃ saṃsitaṃ, nekaṃ kappasahassaṃ saṃsitaṃ, nekaṃ kappasatasahassaṃ saṃsitaṃ. "
msgstr "And we’ve transmigrated through many such eons, many hundreds, many thousands, many hundreds of thousands. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn15.5:2.8"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu? "
msgstr "Why is that? "

msgctxt "sn15.5:2.9"
msgid "Anamataggoyaṃ, bhikkhu, saṃsāro. "
msgstr "Transmigration has no known beginning. … "

msgctxt "sn15.5:2.10"
msgid "Pubbā koṭi … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn15.5:2.11"
msgid "yāvañcidaṃ, bhikkhu, alameva sabbasaṅkhāresu nibbindituṃ, alaṃ virajjituṃ, alaṃ vimuccitun”ti. "
msgstr "This is quite enough for you to become disillusioned, dispassionate, and freed regarding all conditions.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn15.5:2.12"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

